    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Caution: This game is not meant to be medical advice. It's also not very fun.</h2><br>A chronic illness simulation game.<br><br>You think you have a chronic illness, but you don't know what. All you know is you are always in some state of pain. You've been to too many doctors to count... but you still have to live your life.<br><br>How long will it take for you to get a diagnosis?<br><br>Play time is ~30 minutes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224310/extras/c0e6d86f2441fa2b101204c0a84ca095.poster.avif?t=1770039068\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224310/extras/c0e6d86f2441fa2b101204c0a84ca095.webm?t=1770039068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224310/extras/c0e6d86f2441fa2b101204c0a84ca095.mp4?t=1770039068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stressful schedule management as you try to balance living your life and dealing with pain<br></li><li>Different doctors who tell you your chronic pain is made up<br></li><li>Cool and minimal soundtrack by sdhizumi</li></ul>",
